## 📏 SPACING GUIDELINES

### **Use Gap When**

- Flex/Grid containers with 3+ children
- Consistent spacing across all children
- Responsive layouts
- Cleaner code maintenance

### **Use Margin When**

- Single element spacing
- Asymmetric spacing (top ≠ bottom)
- Negative spacing
- Responsive exceptions
- Complex positioning

---

### **SHARED CLASSES CATALOG (USE THESE FIRST)**

#### **Section Patterns**

```css
.section           /* Base section padding */
.section-dark      /* Dark gradient background */
.section-header    /* Centered header with spacing */
.section-title     /* Large responsive title */
.section-description /* Medium description text */
```

#### **Component Patterns**

.(base class) .(type/classification) .(effect/interaction)

```css
.badge .badge-primary .effect-badge
.btn .btn-primary .effect-btn
.card .card-feature .card-hover
.icon .icon-feature .icon-hover

```

#### **Smart Variable Replacement Rules**

**🧠 Auto-Replacement Logic:**

- **Missing Variables** → Use closest semantic equivalent
- **Deprecated Variables** → Map to current standard
- **Generic Variables** → Use specific semantic alternatives

**🔍 Smart Selection Priority:**

1. **Exact semantic match** (same meaning, different name)
2. **Closest functional equivalent** (similar use case)
3. **Size-based mapping** (xs→xs, sm→sm, md→md, lg→lg, xl→xl)
4. **Purpose-based mapping** (text→color, spacing→gap, border→radius)

**⚡ Quick Reference:**

- **Colors**: `--main-color-[1-9]` (semantic hierarchy)
- **Spacing**: `--gap-[xs-sm-md-lg-xl]` (universal spacing)
- **Typography**: `--font-[xs-sm-md-lg-xl]` (responsive sizing)
- **Effects**: `--transition-[fast-normal-slow]` (timing)
- **Shapes**: `--radius-[xs-sm-md-lg-xl]` (corners)

